<!doctype html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Proposal Submission Confirmation - <%= title %></title>
  </head>

  <body
    style="
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 20px;
    "
  >
    <div
      style="
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        max-width: 600px;
        background-color: #fff;
      "
    >
      <div style="text-align: center; padding: 30px">
        <img
          src="https://utfs.io/f/7569a78d-1118-40e6-a844-bfc5433fcb83-yko3op.png"
          alt="GFE Logo"
          style="max-width: 150px"
        />
      </div>
      <div
        style="
          width: calc(100% - 20px);
          height: 1px;
          background-color: #eee;
          margin: 0 10px;
        "
      ></div>

      <div
        style="
          padding: 20px;
          margin: auto;
          background-color: #fff;
          font-size: 10pt;
        "
      >
        <p>Hello, <%= name %></p>
        <p>
          We hope this message finds you well. We're writing to confirm that
          your proposal titled <a href="<%= link %>"><%= title %></a> has been
          successfully submitted to our forum for review. We acknowledge the
          effort and thought you've put into your submission, and we want to
          thank you for actively participating in our DAO community.
        </p>

        <p>
          Your proposal will now undergo a review process. Our administrators
          will carefully assess its adherence to our guidelines and its
          potential impact on our community. The review period typically takes
          3-5 business days, and we will keep you updated on the progress.
        </p>

        <p>
          Should you have any questions or wish to make further amendments to
          your proposal during the review period, please don't hesitate to reach
          out to us.
        </p>

        <p>Thank you once again for your valuable contribution!</p>

        <p>
          Warm regards,<br />
          GFE Foundation Community
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
